### =====================================================================
### Dashboard API  (base route: api/dashboard/)
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### ReadSystemMetrics (no body required)
POST {{host}}/api/dashboard/ReadSystemMetrics

### Read - dashboard data (no body required)
POST {{host}}/api/dashboard/Read

### ReadFinancialOpsDashboard - with date range
POST {{host}}/api/dashboard/ReadFinancialOpsDashboard
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "fromDate": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "toDate": "2026-07-05T00:00:00Z"
}

### ReadPropertyDashboard - default window (null dates)
POST {{host}}/api/dashboard/ReadPropertyDashboard
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}"
}

### ReadOsMetrics
POST {{host}}/api/dashboard/ReadOsMetrics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}"
}

### Enums (GET - lists all tag enums)
GET {{host}}/api/dashboard/Enums
